cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.NA, cs.SD 

The paper deals with image processing and segmentation of microscopy images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of wavelets is also a common technique in image processing and analysis, which suggests the paper could also fit into the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR) or multimedia (cs.MM). The application of the method to locate gold nanoparticles in natural rubber samples suggests a possible fit with numerical analysis (cs.NA) or scientific computing (cs.SD).
